*ser2net-2.2-r1 (18 Mar 2005)

  18 Mar 2005; Rajiv Aaron Manglani <rajiv@gentoo.org>
  +files/ser2net-2.2-tcpwrappers-configure.in.patch, +ser2net-2.2-r1.ebuild:
  ser2net does not actually depend on glib, bug #85569. also make tcp wrappers
  support optional via the tcpd USE flag.

